The '''Crossbow Shop''' in [[Keldagrim Palace]] is a [[Crossbow stall]] owned by [[Hirko]] that sells [[crossbow (weapon)|crossbows]] and crossbow components like other [[crossbow shops]]. It is located in the eastern side of the palace. By talking directly to Hirko, one may also purchase a [[Bolt pouch]].

